# Netflix Clone

A simple Netflix homepage clone built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It includes a responsive layout and an interactive FAQ accordion section.

## Project Structure
- index.html → Main page
- style.css → Styles
- index.js → FAQ accordion functionality

## Features
- Netflix-style landing page design
- Responsive layout for desktop and mobile
- Expandable/collapsible FAQ section with smooth transitions

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
